snippet.textDisplay:
Some say rap is good, some say rap ruined it! 
Both are right, it depends on the taste of music. Being a rajasthani I feel the rap is irrelevant and doesn't suit with a 'bhajan' which is in Core Rajasthani. Some people might think different. Anyway good attempt by Ram to do a fusion but the fusion didn't work out that well. Bhanwari devi's part and Hard Kaur's part heard separately made sense though!
